s.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Attribution</h4>\n<p>Any use of the ROS trademarks needs to include this attribution in your communication: ROS [and/or the “nine dots” ROS logo and/or any other ROS trademark used] is a trademark of Open Robotics.</p>\n<h4>Color specifications</h4>\n<p>For permitted uses of the logo, the color value for print is 533C and the online hex color is #22314E.</p>\";}s:6:\"k33ry1\";a:1:{s:15:\"widgetizer_area\";s:13:\"otw-sidebar-2\";}}s:5:\"draft\";a:8:{s:13:\"page-template\";s:12:\"rosotherpage\";s:10:\"custom-map\";a:1:{s:8:\"template\";a:1:{i:0;a:7:{s:4:\"name\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"class\";s:0:\"\";s:2:\"id\";s:13:\"pl_area94dae8\";s:6:\"object\";s:13:\"PLSectionArea\";s:3:\"sid\";s:7:\"pl_area\";s:5:\"clone\";s:6:\"94dae8\";s:7:\"content\";a:2:{i:0;a:7:{s:6:\"object\";s:8:\"PLColumn\";s:5:\"clone\";s:6:\"1a0bd7\";s:3:\"sid\";s:8:\"plcolumn\";s:4:\"span\";s:1:\"2\";s:6:\"offset\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"newrow\";s:4:\"true\";s:7:\"content\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:6:\"object\";s:19:\"PageLinesWidgetizer\";s:5:\"clone\";s:6:\"k33ry1\";s:3:\"sid\";s:10:\"widgetizer\";s:4:\"span\";s:2:\"12\";s:6:\"offset\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"newrow\";s:5:\"false\";}}}i:1;a:7:{s:6:\"object\";s:8:\"PLColumn\";s:5:\"clone\";s:6:\"1a0c5e\";s:3:\"sid\";s:8:\"plcolumn\";s:4:\"span\";s:1:\"9\";s:6:\"offset\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"newrow\";s:5:\"false\";s:7:\"content\";a:1:{i:0;a:6:{s:6:\"object\";s:16:\"PageLinesTextBox\";s:5:\"clone\";s:6:\"uhkxqp\";s:3:\"sid\";s:7:\"textbox\";s:4:\"span\";s:2:\"12\";s:6:\"offset\";s:1:\"0\";s:6:\"newrow\";s:5:\"false\";}}}}}}}s:6:\"13fdwz\";a:8:{s:12:\"navbar_theme\";s:4:\"base\";s:11:\"navbar_menu\";s:1:\"6\";s:19:\"navbar_enable_hover\";s:1:\"0\";s:24:\"navbar_enable_hover-flip\";s:1:\"0\";s:16:\"navbar_alignment\";s:1:\"0\";s:21:\"navbar_alignment-flip\";s:1:\"0\";s:17:\"navbar_hidesearch\";s:1:\"0\";s:22:\"navbar_hidesearch-flip\";s:1:\"0\";}s:6:\"gequlx\";a:2:{s:15:\"simple_nav_menu\";s:1:\"6\";s:16:\"simple_nav_align\";s:4:\"left\";}s:6:\"i2d7ua\";a:1:{s:15:\"wid